(5, 'View Backer Home Page', 'Code Monkey Save World: Downloads & Order Confirmation', 'Hi there and thank you again for supporting Code Monkey Save World!\r\n\r\nFrom now on most of our communications will be coming from this email address, which is connected to the Code Monkey Save World order fulfillment supercomputer. Please make sure that you''ve added this email address to your address book and (if you''re using gmail) dragged the message into the primary tab if that''s where you''d prefer to read it.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nYOUR BACKER HOME PAGE\r\n\r\nBelow you''ll find a link to your "Backer Home Page", which includes a summary of all the delectable rewards we''ll be delivering to you in the coming months. Depending on the rewards you selected, you may find that digital downloads for some of your rewards are already live!\r\n\r\nhttps://secure.jonathancoulton.com/cmsw/backer_home.php?accesstoken=[:BackerAccessToken:]\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nPlease look over your Backer Home Page and confirm that all rewards you are expecting to receive are listed there. Respond to this email if you have any questions about your rewards!\r\n\r\nAs downloads go live and shipping details are released, we''ll notify you and update your backer home page.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nThank you again for your support!\r\n\r\nTHE CMSW DATA ENTRY MONKEYS\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nP.S. Having trouble viewing the page? Check it out in the latest version of Chrome, Safari or Firefox or reply to this email for more support.', '<p>Hi there and thank you again for supporting Code Monkey Save World!</p>\r\n<p><strong>From now on most of our communications will be coming from this email address</strong>, which is connected to the Code Monkey Save World order fulfillment supercomputer. <strong>Please make sure that you''ve added this email address to your address book</strong> and (if you''re using gmail) dragged the message into the primary tab if that''s where you''d prefer to read it.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>YOUR BACKER HOME PAGE</strong></p>\r\n<p>Below you''ll find a link to your "Backer Home Page", which includes a summary of all the delectable rewards we''ll be delivering to you in the coming months. Depending on the rewards you selected, you may find that digital downloads for some of your rewards are already live!</p>\r\n<p><a href="https://secure.jonathancoulton.com/cmsw/backer_home.php?accesstoken=[:BackerAccessToken:]">https://secure.jonathancoulton.com/cmsw/backer_home.php?accesstoken=[:BackerAccessToken:]</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Please look over your Backer Home Page and confirm that all rewards you are expecting to receive are listed there.</strong> Respond to this email if you have any questions about your rewards!</p>\r\n<p>As downloads go live and shipping details are released, we''ll notify you and update your backer home page.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Thank you again for your support!</p>\r\n<p>THE CMSW DATA ENTRY MONKEYS</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>P.S. Having trouble viewing the page? Check it out in the latest version of Chrome, Safari or Firefox or reply to this email for more support.</p>', 'Default', '2013-08-09 01:18:31', 2);
