('$10.00 USD reward', 'DigitalSoundtrack10', 'The official SOUNDTRACK. Get all of the original Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the graphic novel in one digital package. Includes nifty cover art and the songs "Code Monkey," "Skullcrusher Mountain," "Chiron Beta Prime," "The Future Soon," "Curl," "I Crush Everything," "Creepy Doll," "Re: Your Brains," and maybe even "Good Morning Tucson" if that newscaster character makes it into the book. Also includes the BRAND NEW JONATHAN COULTON SONG and its source tracks!', '10.00', '', '0.00'),
('$100.00 USD reward', 'JoCoMusicPakComixAndBook100', 'ALL OF JONATHAN COULTON''S MUSIC and MORE PAK COMIX plus BOOK & MUSIC! A digital download of Jonathan Coulton''s entire musical ouvre! That''s right, all of his songs (except the Christmas album). PLUS PDFs of several rarely-seen Greg Pak short comic book stories, including "The Citizen," illustrated by Bernard Chang and the "Rio Chino" stories illustrated by Ian Kim and Sean Chen. PLUS the gorgeous hard copy of the "Code Monkey Save World" graphic novel! PLUS the digital downloads of the chapters through Monkeybrain and comiXology. PLUS a digital download of the soundtrack, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book! Add $10 for shipping outside the US.', '100.00', '', '10.00'),
