('$125.00 USD reward', 'DIYFigurineBookMusic125', 'CODE MONKEY FIGURINE DIY KIT plus BOOK & MUSIC. Yes, the $200 limited edition, painted resin figurines of Code Monkey sculpted by the brilliant artist Sean Chen have SOLD OUT. But now you can get a special DO-IT-YOURSELF KIT that includes six cast resin pieces and instructions on how to assemble them into the finished Code Monkey figurine! (You''ll need your own X-acto knife, sandpaper, superglue and paint.) PLUS we promise to post pictures you send us of your assembled and painted figurine on the "Code Monkey Save World" web page when it''s live later in the year (pictures must be SFW, natch). PLUS you get the gorgeous physical copy of the "Code Monkey Save World" trade paperback! PLUS the digital downloads of the chapters through Monkeybrain and comiXology. PLUS a digital download of the soundtrack, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book! Add $25 for shipping outside the US.', '125.00', '', '25.00'),
('$15.00 USD reward', 'DigitalBookRelease15', 'DIGITAL BOOK RELEASE plus MUSIC. For just fifteen bucks, you get digital downloads of each of the four chapters of the "Code Monkey Save World" graphic novel as they''re completed through Monkeybrain Comics and comiXology. Each issue available exclusively to Kickstarter backers for the first month of release. We''re hoping to start releasing issues in August, finish in November. PLUS a digital download of the SOUNDTRACK, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book!', '15.00', '', '0.00'),
('$150.00 USD reward 1', 'Retailers10SignedBooksAndAd150', 'RETAILERS ONLY! Ten copies of the "Code Monkey Save World" graphic novel, SIGNED by Greg Pak and Jonathan Coulton! Plus a bunch of stickers and buttons. PLUS an ADVERTISEMENT for your store in the print edition of the "Code Monkey Save World" graphic novel! PLUS a digital download of ALL OF JONATHAN COULTON''S SONGS! That''s right, all of them (except the Christmas album). PLUS the digital downloads of the chapters through Monkeybrain and comiXology. PLUS a digital download of the soundtrack, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book! Add $60 for shipping outside the US.', '150.00', '', '60.00'),
('$150.00 USD reward 2', 'AdvertisementAndBook150', 'Get your own ADVERTISEMENT in the hard copy print edition of the "Code Monkey Save World" graphic novel! Yep, you''ll get a space approximately two square inches for a message of your choosing on a special page in the actual graphic novel. (No pornography, profanity, hate speech, illegal or mean-spirited stuff in the messages or ads allowed, natch.) PLUS the gorgeous hard copy of the "Code Monkey Save World" graphic novel! PLUS the digital downloads of the chapters through Monkeybrain and comiXology. PLUS a digital download of the soundtrack, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book! Add $10 for shipping outside the US.', '150.00', '', '10.00'),
('$150.00 USD reward 3', 'R2AdvertisementAndBook150', 'SECOND BONUS ROUND! 30 MORE AVAILABLE! Get your own ADVERTISEMENT in the hard copy print edition of the "Code Monkey Save World" graphic novel! Yep, you''ll get a space approximately two square inches for a message of your choosing on a special page in the actual graphic novel. (No pornography, profanity, hate speech, illegal or mean-spirited stuff in the messages or ads allowed, natch.) PLUS the gorgeous hard copy of the "Code Monkey Save World" trade paperback! PLUS the digital downloads of the chapters through Monkeybrain and comiXology. PLUS a digital download of the soundtrack, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book! Add $10 for shipping outside the US.', '150.00', '', '10.00'),
('$150.00 USD reward 4', 'PakVoicemailJoCoSongsPakComixAndBook150', 'PAK VOICEMAIL MESSAGE plus MORE OF GREG''S COMICS plus ALL OF JONATHAN''S SONGS (except the Christmas album) plus BOOK & MUSIC. Yeah, the Jonathan Coulton voicemail messages are sold out. But here''s your chance to have Greg Pak record an outgoing message for your voicemail or phone based on a script provided by you! No, Greg is not a professional singer-songwriter on the internet. But he''s been told he has a very nice speaking voice -- he even did radio in college! (No pornography, profanity, hate speech, illegal or really creepy or mean-spirited stuff in the messages allowed, natch.) Message will be delivered in mp3 format. PLUS PDFs of several rarely-seen Greg Pak short comic book stories, including "The Citizen," illustrated by Bernard Chang and the "Rio Chino" stories illustrated by Ian Kim and Sean Chen. PLUS a digital download of ALL OF JONATHAN COULTON''S SONGS! That''s right, all of them (except the Christmas album). PLUS the gorgeous hard copy of the "Code Monkey Save World" trade paperback! PLUS the digital downloads of the chapters through Monkeybrain and comiXology. PLUS a digital download of the soundtrack, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book! Add $10 for shipping outside the US.', '150.00', '', '10.00'),
('$150.00 USD reward 5', 'R3AdvertisementAndBook150', 'THIRD BONUS ROUND! 30 MORE AVAILABLE! Get your own ADVERTISEMENT in the hard copy print edition of the "Code Monkey Save World" graphic novel! Yep, you''ll get a space approximately two square inches for a message of your choosing on a special page in the actual graphic novel. (No pornography, profanity, hate speech, illegal or mean-spirited stuff in the messages or ads allowed, natch.) PLUS the gorgeous hard copy of the "Code Monkey Save World" trade paperback! PLUS the digital downloads of the chapters through Monkeybrain and comiXology. PLUS a digital download of the soundtrack, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book! Add $10 for shipping outside the US.', '150.00', '', '10.00'),
('$160.00 USD reward', 'SuperSwagBundle160', 'SUPER SWAG BUNDLE - Includes the T-SHIRT, MUG, POSTER, and CHALLENGE COINS plus everything in the $35 pledge level PLUS THREE MORE CHALLENGE COINS (each featuring a new, different design!) PLUS ALL OF JONATHAN COULTON''S MUSIC (minus the Christmas album) PLUS the signed "Code Monkey Save World" script! Add $70 for shipping outside the US.', '160.00', '', '70.00'),
('$200.00 USD reward', 'JoCoVoicemailJoCoSongs200', 'COULTON VOICEMAIL MESSAGE plus ALL OF JONATHAN''S SONGS (except the Christmas album) plus BOOK & MUSIC. Jonathan Coulton will record an outgoing message for your voicemail or phone based on a script provided by you. (No pornography, profanity, hate speech, illegal or really creepy or mean-spirited stuff in the messages allowed, natch.) HE MIGHT EVEN SING IT FOR YOU, YO! Message will be delivered in mp3 format. PLUS a digital download of ALL OF JONATHAN COULTON''S SONGS! That''s right, all of them (except the Christmas album). PLUS the gorgeous hard copy of the "Code Monkey Save World" trade paperback! PLUS the digital downloads of the chapters through Monkeybrain and comiXology. PLUS a digital download of the soundtrack, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book! Add $10 for shipping outside the US.', '200.00', '', '10.00'),
('$25.00 USD reward', 'TradePaperback25', 'HARD COPY TRADE PAPERBACK plus DIGITAL BOOKS plus MUSIC! Get the gorgeous hard copy of the "Code Monkey Save World" graphic novel PLUS the digital downloads of the chapters through Monkeybrain and comiXology. PLUS a digital download of the soundtrack, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book! Add $10 for shipping outside the US.', '25.00', '', '10.00'),
('$250.00 USD reward', 'SecretInsiderPackage250', 'CODE MONKEY SECRET INSIDER PACKAGE. This is a craaaaazy idea, but we think you''re going to like it. Pledge at this level and we will include you in a super-secret mailing list wherein you will get an incredibly in-depth, advance look at every stage of the production of the comic book as it''s being created. This means... hold onto your hats, now... you''ll get the scripts ahead of time. You''ll see select pencils, inks, and colors as they come in. You''ll see some of the first lettering drafts and some of the final polished letters. In short, you''ll see how this comic is being made and the creative decisions that are going into it IN REAL TIME. You''ll start receiving stuff in May and will continue getting super secret insider emails until the book''s completed at the end of the year. AND you''ll get the gorgeous hard copy of the "Code Monkey Save World" graphic novel! PLUS the digital downloads of the chapters through Monkeybrain and comiXology. PLUS a digital download of the soundtrack, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book! (PLEASE NOTE: To receive this reward, you will have to sign a non-disclosure agreement promising not to release any of the super-secret stuff we''re sharing with you unless and until you get written approval from us.)', '250.00', '', '0.00'),
('$3.00 USD reward', 'DomesticStickers3', 'STICKERS! Yes, if all you have is three bucks, WE WILL TAKE IT. And we''ll send you some official "Code Monkey Save World" stickers via the US mail! EVERYBODY LOVES STICKERS!', '3.00', 'Domestic', '0.00'),
