('$300.00 USD reward 1', 'SignedFigurineJoCoMusic300', 'CODE MONKEY FIGURINE plus ALL JOCO SONGS plus BOOK & MUSIC. A limited edition resin figurine of Code Monkey sculpted by the brilliant artist Sean Chen, numbered and signed by Chen, Pak, and Coulton! PLUS a digital download of ALL OF JONATHAN COULTON''S SONGS! That''s right, all of them (except the Christmas album). PLUS the gorgeous hard copy of the "Code Monkey Save World" trade paperback! PLUS the digital downloads of the chapters through Monkeybrain and comiXology. PLUS a digital download of the soundtrack, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book! Add $25 for shipping outside the US.', '300.00', '', '25.00'),
('$300.00 USD reward 2', 'CasualFridaySignedFigurineJoCoMusic300', 'SECOND BONUS ROUND! "CASUAL FRIDAY" VARIANT CODE MONKEY FIGURINE plus ALL JOCO SONGS plus BOOK & MUSIC. A limited edition resin figurine of Code Monkey sculpted by the brilliant artist Sean Chen, numbered and signed by Chen, Pak, and Coulton! This is the second round, "Casual Friday" Code Monkey variant version, who wears blue rather than khaki pants. PLUS a digital download of ALL OF JONATHAN COULTON''S SONGS! That''s right, all of them (except the Christmas album). PLUS the gorgeous hard copy of the "Code Monkey Save World" trade paperback! PLUS the digital downloads of the chapters through Monkeybrain and comiXology. PLUS a digital download of the soundtrack, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book! Add $25 for shipping outside the US.', '300.00', '', '25.00'),
