('$500.00 USD reward 1', 'LikenessAndPanel500', 'Have your likeness drawn into the "Code Monkey Save World" graphic novel as a supporting character! AND get the original panel from the Takeshi Miyazawa page that your likeness appears on! (Please note that you''ll have to sign a release form authorizing us to use your likeness.) PLUS the gorgeous hard copy of the "Code Monkey Save World" graphic novel! PLUS the digital downloads of the chapters through Monkeybrain and comiXology. PLUS a digital download of the soundtrack, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book! Add $10 for shipping outside the US.', '500.00', '', '10.00'),
