('$75.00 USD reward', 'SignedScriptBookAndMusic75', 'SIGNED SCRIPT AND MORE JOCO MUSIC plus BOOK & MUSIC! The script of the "Code Monkey Save World" graphic novel, SIGNED BY GREG PAK. PLUS all of Jonathan Coulton''s classic and beloved "Thing a Week" songs in digital form. That''s 52 songs, y''all. PLUS the gorgeous hard copy of the "Code Monkey Save World" graphic novel! PLUS the digital downloads of the chapters through Monkeybrain and comiXology. PLUS a digital download of the soundtrack, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book! Add $15 for shipping outside the US.', '75.00', '', '15.00'),
('$750.00 USD reward', 'JoCoRecordingSessionMugTshirtPosterSignedScriptBook750', 'SEE JONATHAN COULTON RECORD THE "CODE MONKEY SAVE WORLD" ACOUSTIC ALBUM LIVE IN NYC! This is nuts. At this level, you and a guest can come to the studio in New York City to watch part of Jonathan Coulton''s recording session for the new acoustic album! We''ll even take you to lunch. Exact date TBA -- but probably some time in June. Travel to New York and accomodations, etcetera not included. But this does include the MUG, the T-SHIRT, the POSTER, and the SIGNED SCRIPT. PLUS a digital download of ALL OF JONATHAN COULTON''S SONGS! That''s right, all of them (except the Christmas album). PLUS the gorgeous hard copy of the "Code Monkey Save World" trade paperback! PLUS the digital downloads of the chapters through Monkeybrain and comiXology. PLUS a digital download of the soundtrack, which includes all the Jonathan Coulton songs that inspired the book! PLUS a digital download of the NEW JoCo song inspired by the book! (Also, don''t worry -- if we don''t reach the stretch goal enabling the album and we don''t record it, your money will be refunded.)', '750.00', 'UNKNOWN', '0.00'),
